column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,  p.deVRad_u,p.deVRadErr_u, p.deVRad_z,p.deVRadErr_z, g.lgm_tot_p5#,   p.z,p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE   s.class = &&&  AND g.lgm_tot_p5# > #  AND s.z Between # AND #
